title: Shane Mauss
description: Shane Mauss (Conan! Kimmel! Comedy!) is one of Pete's all time favorite comedians and is an incredible YMIW guest. So many stories, so many laughs and so much science and psychology you can't even believe it. FREE PODCAST?! Enjoy you weirdos!!
